        <updateDate>2021-08-19T14:18:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Conveyance Capacity Correction Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows the Bureau of Reclamation to provide funding to repair certain water conveyance facilities that (1) need nonrecurring repairs because of damage caused by land subsidence; (2) have lost a specified portion of their designed carrying capacity; or (3) would, with restored carrying capacity, assist in meeting groundwater sustainability goals.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
